Fred Groves (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Fred_Groves_(actor) 0 Fred Groves (8 August 1880 – 4 June 1955) was a British actor. On stage from 1896, he appeared in the original West End production of Noël Coward's Cavalcade (1931-2); and was a leading man in silent films, latterly becoming a character player in movies.
